At TD SYNNEX, we're proud to be recognized as a great place to work and a leader in the promotion and practice of diversity, equity and inclusion. If you're excited about working for our company and believe you're a good fit for this role, we encourage you to apply. You may be exactly the person we're looking for!

About the Team

We are Quadcode, a fintech company excelling in financial brokerage activities and delivering advanced financial products to our global clientele. Our flagship product, an internal trading platform, is offered as a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) solution to other brokers.

We are looking for a Junior Creative Marketing Producer to help elevate the quality and performance of our marketing content by increasing the share of top-performing creatives within the overall production output.
Tasks:
Organize and manage the marketing content production process, including videos, UGC, banners, landing pages, and playables, working with internal production teams, outsourced agencies, and freelance platforms such as Fiverr and Upwork;
Create, maintain, and update marketing network guidelines, marketing product guidelines, and geo-specific regulatory requirements in collaboration with traffic managers;
Conduct competitor analysis to identify trends, benchmarks, and creative opportunities;
Collect, analyze, and interpret marketing performance statistics to improve creative effectiveness;
Participate in the development of global and regional marketing strategies for the brand;
Plan production timelines and ensure deadlines are met to achieve key marketing and departmental goals.
Requirements:
Strong organizational and coordination skills;
Analytical mindset with the ability to work with marketing performance data;
Understanding of digital marketing content formats and performance drivers;
Ability to work with multiple stakeholders and manage parallel tasks;
Good communication skills and a proactive attitude;
Interest in marketing, creative production, and performance-driven content.
Nice to Have:
Experience using AI content generation tools such as ChatGPT, ElevenLabs, VEO, Kling, Sora, or similar services;
Basic understanding of paid traffic or performance marketing workflows;
Experience working with creative agencies or freelance platforms.
What we offer:
Remote work model;
Competitive remuneration;
Friendly, enjoyable and positive environment.
With a team of 500+ creative and tech-driven people across the globe, Quadcode is the place where ideas turn into impact, where every project is a chance to grow, innovate, and make your mark.

Join us today, and let's shape the future of fintech together!

Note: All applications will be treated with strict confidence. We thank all applicants for their interest, however, only those candidates selected for interviews will be contacted.

